  • Classes in fr.sorbonne_u.components.annotations used by bcm.node.accesspoint.components 
    Class Description
    OfferedInterfaces
    The annotation OfferedInterface put on a component definition class tells BCM that this component is offering all of the interfaces given in the array.
    RequiredInterfaces
    The annotation RequiredInterface put on a component definition class tells BCM that this component is requiring all of the interfaces given in the array.
